
After graduating from middle school its time to put your big boy pants on. With your four best friends, Dylan, lem, Scott and kyle. You have a secret that weighed you down ......... your gay.
When you decide to come out, all the while staring at that sexy hunk Scott, will you still be brothers in arms? As secrets are reveled with one of your friends in the mist of it all, will you be able to except the wolf that calls you mate, or will you join the enemies or your mate, Dark Forest, where your corrupted wolf thinks it truly belongs?
'Not all things are what it seems, if you think you've figured out what will happen next.......YOU HAVEN'T'